<h2>Welcome to the Snups tutorial!</h2>
<ol>
    <li>First you hit the Registrationbutton to sign up.</li>
    <li>After Sign up you can go to the android market and download Snups.</li>
    <li>Open the app on your mobilephone and login.</li>
    <li>When you are logged in you get a new mission.</li>
    <li>If you don't like your current mission you can press the "new mission" button</li>
    <li>Otherwise you can push the "play" button</li>
    <li>Then you see through your camera and can take a picture which fits your topic</li>
    <li>After you have taken your picture you can either choose take new picture or upload your current image.</li>
</ol>



